# Shared Components

`src/app/shared/` may contain only generic reusable UI and utilities.

## Allowed examples

Button, Input, Modal, Drawer, DataTable, Pagination, SearchBar, StatusBadge, Tabs, Card, PageHeader, EmptyState, Loader, LoadingState, Toast, ConfirmDialog, AppLayout, Sidebar, TopNavbar, AuthLayout, apiClient, date/validation/formatting utils, roles/statuses/routes constants.

## Forbidden examples

AssetCard, BookingCalendar, MaintenanceKanban, AuditChecklist, TransferRequestForm, DepartmentTable, and any other feature-specific component.

## Rules

- Feature-specific components must remain inside their module.
- Before adding anything to shared, verify it is domain-neutral and useful to at least two modules.
- Shared is protected; prefer asking the integrator before expanding it.
